name: An Antique Edwardian Celluloid Hair Comb Pick
description:
An Antique Edwardian celluloid hair comb/pick.  Celluloid was used for creating less expensive jewellery, hair accessories and many items that would earlier have been manufactured from ivory, horn or other expensive animal products.  The hair pic/comb resembles tortoiseshell.  It is mottled and translucent.   It measures approximately 10.3 cm in length by 5.3 cm wide, at it's widest points.  The hair pic/comb is decorated with faux stones.  

It is in good vintage condition, with some minor scratches to the celluloid.  Please refer to the photographs.

name: Vogue Italia Gennaio 2005 Italian Vogue January 2005 Fashion Magazine
description:
A copy of Vogue Italia Gennaio 2005 - Italian Vogue January 2005

Cover: Steven Meisel HOLLYWOOD (a double cover)

Issue: 653

The issue includes: 

CELEBRITY. Foto di Steven Meisel.  Fashion editor Edward Enninful

Vogue On The Stage Londra Milano New York Parigi Fashion Shows A-Z

Vogue Beauty 7 Icons: Foto di David LaChapelle, Vincent Peters, Michael Thompson, Max Vadukul, Karl Largerfeld, Peter Lindbergh, Stephane Sednaoui.

Condition/flaws to note: 

It is in good clean pre-owned condition.  All of the pages are present.  
There is some discolouration to the edges of the pages due to age and having been stored.  
There are some light surface scratches to the back cover, please see photo 5.
There is slight wear to the crease on the double cover.

Please note these magazines are pre-owned, they have been read and stored for some time.  They are lovely items but do show minimal wear.   

The magazine is a great fashion, make up, hair and photography reference.

* Please note it is not possible to combine postage for the magazines.  It is actually less expensive to post them individually due to their weight.
